{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-287-quadtree-encoding-a-simple-compression-algorithm","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 287: Indeksiranje quadtree (jednostavan algoritam kodiranja)","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Enkodovanje kvadstabla daje namogućnost predstavljanja crno-belu sliku $2^N×2^N$ kao niz bitova (0 i 1). Taj niz se čita od leve ka desnoj, kao što sledi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>prvi bit se odnosi na celokupno područje $2^N×2^N$;</li>\n<li>\"0\" ukazuje na podelu:\n<ul>\n<li>trenutno područje $2^n×2^n$ je podeljeno na 4 manja područja dimenzija $2^{n - 1}×2^{n - 1}$,</li>\n<li>sledeći bitovi opisuju mala područja gore levo, gore desno, dole levo i dole desno – u tom redosledu;</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\"10\" ukazuje da trenutno područje sadrži samo crne piksele;</li>\n<li>\"11\" ukazuje da trenutno područje sadrži samo bele piksele.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Gledajte sledeću sliku od 4×4 (boje označavaju mesta gde može doći do podele):</p>\n<img alt=\"4x4 image with colored marks denoting place where split can occur\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/quadtree-encoding-a-simple-compression-algorithm.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Ova slika se može opisati nekoliko sekvenci, na primer: \"<strong><span style=\"color: red\">0</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue\">0</span></strong>10101010<strong><span style=\"color: green\">0</span></strong>1011111011<strong><span style=\"color: orange\">0</span></strong>10101010\", dužine 30, ili \"<strong><span style=\"color: red\">0</span></strong>10<strong><span style=\"color: green\">0</span></strong>101111101110\", dužine 16, što je najkraća sekvenca za ovu sliku.</p>\n<p>Za pozitivno $N$, definiše se $D_N$ kao sliku od $2^N×2^N$ sa rasporedom boja kao što sledi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pikseli sa koordinatama $x = 0$, $y = 0$ su pikseli donjeg levog ugla,</li>\n<li>Ako je ${(x - 2^{N - 1})}^2 + {(y - 2^{N - 1})}^2 ≤ 2^{2N - 2}$, onda je piksel crn,</li>\n<li>Inače je piksel beli.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Koja je dužina najkraće sekvence koja opisuje $D_{24}?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f48b1000cf542c50ff9e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301938,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-287-quadtree-encoding-a-simple-compression-algorithm"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function quadtreeEncoding() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nquadtreeEncoding();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>quadtreeEncoding()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>313135496</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(quadtreeEncoding(), 313135496);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-287-quadtree-encoding-a-simple-compression-algorithm","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-288-an-enormous-factorial","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-286-scoring-probabilities","id":"5900f48b1000cf542c50ff9e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview